<template>
    <v-container>
      <v-form ref="form" v-model="valid">
        <v-text-field v-model="record.cpf" label="CPF" :rules="[rules.required]" outlined></v-text-field>
        <v-text-field v-model="record.name" label="Nome" :rules="[rules.required]" outlined></v-text-field>
        <v-text-field v-model="record.phone" label="Telefone" outlined></v-text-field>
        <v-btn :disabled="!valid" color="success" @click="submit">Salvar</v-btn>
      </v-form>
    </v-container>
  </template>
  
  <script>
  export default {
    data() {
      return {
        valid: true,
        record: {
          cpf: '',
          name: '',
          phone: ''
        },
        rules: {
          required: value => !!value || 'Campo obrigat贸rio.',
        },
      };
    },
    methods: {
      submit() {
        // Implementar l贸gica para enviar dados ao backend
      }
    }
  }
  </script>
